Lucky Hills Shrubland, Arizona, USA
variable or unit conversions

Obs cline
1 * LUCKYHILLS convert co2den from mg/m3 to mmol/m3;
2 co2den = co2den / 44.0;
3 * LUCKYHILLS convert fc from mg/m2/s to umol/m2/s;
4 fc = fc / 0.044;
5 * LUCKYHILLS convert h2oden from g/m3 to mmol/m3;
6 h2oden = h2oden / 18.0 * 1000;


 
Lucky Hills Shrubland, Arizona, USA
calculated or derived variables

Obs cline
1 * LUCKYHILLS calculate co2 from co2den using press and ta;
2 if press not in (.,0) then co2 = co2den*8.314*(ta+273.15)/press; else co2 = .;
3 * LUCKYHILLS calculate h2o from h2oden using press and ta;
4 if press not in (.,0) then h2o = h2oden/1000*8.314*(ta+273.15)/press; else h2o = .;
5 * LUCKYHILLS calculate fh2o from le and ta;
6 fh2o = le/18/(1.91846*((ta+273.15)/(ta+273.15-33.91))*((ta+273.15)/(ta+273.15-33.91)));
7 * LUCKYHILLS calculate svp from ta;
8 svp=0.61121*exp((17.502 * ta)/(240.97 + ta));
9 * LUCKYHILLS calculate rh from vp and svp;
10 rh = (vp/svp)*100;
11 * LUCKYHILLS calculate vpd from svp and vp;
12 vpd = svp - vp;
13 * LUCKYHILLS calculate preccum;
14 preccum = ifn(first.year, prec, sum(preccum, prec));
